match let merlin_path = Fpath.v merlin_path in
      let merlin = Merlin.make merlin_path merlin_frontend in
      let proj_path = Fpath.v (Unix.realpath proj_dir) in
      let data_dir =
        match data_dir with
        | Some dir -> Fpath.v dir
        | None ->
            let proj_name = Fpath.basename proj_path in
            let ts = Int.to_string (Int.of_float (Unix.time ())) in
            Fpath.v ("data/" ^ (proj_name ^ ("+" ^ ts))) in
      let data = Data.init data_dir in
      match File.get_files ~extensions proj_path with
      | Ok files ->
          let side_effectively_add_data (qt, id_counter) (file, query_type) =
            match Samples.generate ~sample_size ~id_counter file query_type
            with
            | None ->
                let log =
                  Data.Logs.Warning
                    (Format.sprintf
                       (CamlinternalFormatBasics.Format
                          ((CamlinternalFormatBasics.String_literal
                              ("File ",
                                (CamlinternalFormatBasics.String
                                   (CamlinternalFormatBasics.No_padding,
                                     (CamlinternalFormatBasics.String_literal
                                        (" couldn't be parsed and was ignored.\n",
                                          CamlinternalFormatBasics.End_of_format)))))),
                            "File %s couldn't be parsed and was ignored.\n"))
                       (Yojson.Safe.to_string ?buf:None ?len:None ?suf:None
                          ?std:None (File.to_yojson file))) in
                (Data.update ?perf:None ?resp:None ?cmd:None ?log:(Some log)
                   ?metadata:None data;
                 (qt, id_counter))
            | Some (samples, new_id_counter) ->
                ((Samples.add_analysis_to_data ~merlin ~query_time:qt
                    ~repeats_per_sample data samples), new_id_counter) in
          let (total_query_time, _last_sample_id) =
            List.fold_over_product ~l1:files ~l2:query_types ~init:(0., 0)
              side_effectively_add_data in
          let metadata =
            let total_time = Sys.time () in
            let source_code_commit_sha =
              match Data.Metadata.get_commit_sha ~proj_dir with
              | Ok sha -> Some sha
              | Error log ->
                  (Data.update ?perf:None ?resp:None ?cmd:None
                     ?log:(Some log) ?metadata:None data;
                   None) in
            let date = Data.Metadata.get_date () in
            {
              Data.Metadata.query_time = total_query_time;
              Data.Metadata.total_time = total_time;
              Data.Metadata.date = date;
              Data.Metadata.source_code_commit_sha = source_code_commit_sha;
              Data.Metadata.merlin = merlin
            } in
          (Data.update ?perf:None ?resp:None ?cmd:None ?log:None
             ?metadata:(Some metadata) data;
           Data.dump data;
           Merlin.stop_server merlin)
      | Error (`Msg err) ->
          (Printf.eprintf
             (CamlinternalFormatBasics.Format
                ((CamlinternalFormatBasics.String
                    (CamlinternalFormatBasics.No_padding,
                      CamlinternalFormatBasics.End_of_format)), "%s")) err;
           exit 50)
with
| () -> _

(match let log =
        Data.Logs.Warning
          (Format.sprintf
             (CamlinternalFormatBasics.Format
                ((CamlinternalFormatBasics.String_literal
                    ("File ",
                      (CamlinternalFormatBasics.String
                         (CamlinternalFormatBasics.No_padding,
                           (CamlinternalFormatBasics.String_literal
                              (" couldn't be parsed and was ignored.\n",
                                CamlinternalFormatBasics.End_of_format)))))),
                  "File %s couldn't be parsed and was ignored.\n"))
             (Yojson.Safe.to_string ?buf:None ?len:None ?suf:None ?std:None
                (File.to_yojson file))) in
      Data.update ?perf:None ?resp:None ?cmd:None ?log:(Some log)
        ?metadata:None data;
      (qt, id_counter)
with
| (_, _) -> _)
